stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_fork: is first block after fork
    q_check_fork --> q_calc_epochs: fork detected
    q_check_fork --> [*]: not first block after fork
    q_calc_epochs --> q_iter: epoch = current_epoch; end = current_epoch + MIN_SEED_LOOKAHEAD
    q_iter --> q_compute: epoch <= end
    q_compute --> q_fill: proposers = get_beacon_proposer_indices(state, epoch)
    q_fill --> q_iter: fill proposer_lookahead segment; epoch = epoch + 1
    q_iter --> [*]: epoch > end; proposer_lookahead fully initialized
